i looked at the error log when Apache wouldn't start and it said '[Fri Nov 22 
20:44:25 2002] [error] [client 127.0.0.1] File does not exist: D:/Program 
Files/Apache Group/Apache2/Apache2/htdocs/check_ip.php3'

That wasn't introduced by the Apache software, so I'm afraid we can't
  be much help.  Try an apporpriate user support forum such as the users
  list or newsgroups.
